{
  "stem": "6526.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That was our plan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Coming into Warsaw ghetto, my friend had a sister and brother-in-law and two nephews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He went to live with them, and I found out that I had cousins live in Warsaw, right in the same street.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A block away in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went to the cousins.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were happy to see me, and I was happy with them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were there since before New Year's till the December 18.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On December 18-- I'm sorry, January.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "January 18, 1943.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On January 18, we heard a lot of commotions.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, we had-- my cousins had prepared themselves in case anything happens, we'll be in the bunkers underneath the buildings.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the entrance and the exit was so masqueraded, that was not easy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You are tired.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Are you tired?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not easy to find out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they knew that we were there because they saw from the smoke or something that people are there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not be able to get us out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There are gates to come into a building.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they threw a bomb in on the floor, on the ground under the gate and that came in-- from the bomb, we got gassed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had entrance to the sewers, on a separate area entered the sewers, so that we can run away outside or inside.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So my cousins and I went in through the sewers and to look for a place to get.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But before that, my brother--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before that, my brother and some of our friends went in across the street to see what the other ones are doing, because there were other people lived across the street, to find what the other ones are doing.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they never came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
